N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16ยง 17.4 - Correction of deficiencies

State Regulations

Deficiencies in a filed petition, when called to the
attention of the applicant, must be promptly corrected, or the application may
be denied for lack of proper submission. Notes
